These tumuli are located about 200 meters northeast of {{ill|Saiseki Shrine|ja|細石神社|12=draft}}, with the {{ill|Hirabaru Site|ja|平原遺跡|12=draft}} approximately 1 kilometer to the northwest. The area is considered a key region of the ancient {{ill|Itokoku|ja|伊都国|1=Itokoku|12=draft}}, as described in the {{ill|Records of Wei|ja|魏志倭人伝|12=draft}}.

